SELECT [c].[KichThuoc], [c].[SoLuong]
FROM [ChiTietKichThuoc] AS [c]
WHERE [c].[MaSanPham] = @__maSP_0
2024-12-02 13:11:02.819 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (20ms) [Parameters=[@__maSP_0='11'], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [d].[DanhGia], [d].[BinhLuan], [d].[id] AS [Id], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c0].[KichThuoc]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [ChiTietKichThuoc] AS [c0] ON ([c].[MaSanPham] = [c0].[MaSanPham]) AND ([c].[MaChiTiet] = [c0].[MaChiTiet])
    WHERE [c].[MaDH] = [d].[MaDH]) AS [KichThuoc], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [c1].[SoLuong]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c1]
    WHERE ([c1].[MaDH] = [d].[MaDH]) AND ([c1].[MaSanPham] = [d].[MaSanPham])), 0) AS [SoLuong], [d].[HinhAnh], [d].[NgayDanhGia], [d].[MaSanPham], [t0].[HoTen] AS [TenKhachHang], (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [DanhGiaSP] AS [d0]
    WHERE [d0].[MaSanPham] = [d].[MaSanPham]) AS [LuotDanhGia], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[PhanHoi]
    FROM [PhanHoiDanhGia] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[MaDanhGia] = [d].[MaDanhGia]) AS [PhanHoi], (
    SELECT COALESCE(SUM([c2].[SoLuong]), 0)
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c2]
    INNER JOIN [DonHang] AS [d1] ON [c2].[MaDH] = [d1].[MaDH]
    WHERE ([c2].[MaSanPham] = @__maSP_0) AND (([d1].[TrangThaiDH] = N'Đã đánh giá') OR (([d1].[TrangThaiDH] = N'Đã Thanh Toán') AND [d1].[ThongTinDH] IN (N'Đã Giao', N'Đang Giao')))) AS [LuotMua]
FROM [DanhGiaSP] AS [d]
INNER JOIN [TaiKhoan] AS [t] ON [d].[id] = [t].[id]
INNER JOIN [ThongTinCaNhan] AS [t0] ON [t].[idTK] = [t0].[idTK]
WHERE [d].[MaSanPham] = @__maSP_0

FROM [ChiTietKhuyenMai] AS [c]
INNER JOIN [KhuyenMai] AS [k] ON [c].[MaVoucher] = [k].[MaVoucher]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s].[MaSanPham], [s].[Gia], [s].[HinhAnh], [s].[MaBoSuuTap], [s].[MaChiTietGiam], [s].[MaLoaiSP], [s].[MaVatLieu], [s].[MoTa], [s].[TenSanPham], [l].[MaLoaiSP] AS [MaLoaiSP0], [l].[Slug], [l].[TenLoaiSP]
    FROM [SanPham] AS [s]
    INNER JOIN [LoaiSP] AS [l] ON [s].[MaLoaiSP] = [l].[MaLoaiSP]
) AS [t] ON ([c].[MaChiTietGiam] = [t].[MaChiTietGiam]) AND ([c].[MaSanPham] = [t].[MaSanPham])
ORDER BY [c].[MaChiTietGiam], [c].[MaSanPham], [k].[MaVoucher], [t].[MaSanPham]

SELECT [c].[MaChiTietGiam], [c].[MaSanPham], [c].[MaVoucher], [c].[Slug], [c].[TenGiamGia], [k].[MaVoucher], [t].[MaSanPham], [t].[Gia], [t].[HinhAnh], [t].[MaBoSuuTap], [t].[MaChiTietGiam], [t].[MaLoaiSP], [t].[MaVatLieu], [t].[MoTa], [t].[TenSanPham], [t].[MaLoaiSP0], [t].[Slug], [t].[TenLoaiSP], [k].[GhiChu], [k].[id], [k].[PhanTramGiam], [k].[SoLan], [k].[TenChuongTrinh], [k].[ThoiGianBatDau], [k].[ThoiGianKetThuc]
FROM [ChiTietKhuyenMai] AS [c]
INNER JOIN [KhuyenMai] AS [k] ON [c].[MaVoucher] = [k].[MaVoucher]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s].[MaSanPham], [s].[Gia], [s].[HinhAnh], [s].[MaBoSuuTap], [s].[MaChiTietGiam], [s].[MaLoaiSP], [s].[MaVatLieu], [s].[MoTa], [s].[TenSanPham], [l].[MaLoaiSP] AS [MaLoaiSP0], [l].[Slug], [l].[TenLoaiSP]
    FROM [SanPham] AS [s]
    INNER JOIN [LoaiSP] AS [l] ON [s].[MaLoaiSP] = [l].[MaLoaiSP]
) AS [t] ON ([c].[MaChiTietGiam] = [t].[MaChiTietGiam]) AND ([c].[MaSanPham] = [t].[MaSanPham])
ORDER BY [c].[MaChiTietGiam], [c].[MaSanPham], [k].[MaVoucher], [t].[MaSanPham]

        FROM [TaiKhoan] AS [t2]
        WHERE [t2].[id] = [g].[id])

    SELECT [s].[TenSanPham], [c].[MaDH], [c].[MaChiTiet], [s].[MaSanPham]

    SELECT TOP(1) (
        SELECT TOP(1) [t2].[TenDangNhap]
        FROM [TaiKhoan] AS [t2]
        WHERE [t2].[id] = [g].[id])
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c4]
    INNER JOIN [GioHang] AS [g] ON [c4].[MaGioHang] = [g].[MaGioHang]
    WHERE [c4].[MaDH] = [d].[MaDH])
FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s].[TenSanPham], [c].[MaDH], [c].[MaChiTiet], [s].[MaSanPham]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [SanPham] AS [s] ON [c].[MaSanPham] = [s].[MaSanPham]
) AS [t] ON [d].[MaDH] = [t].[MaDH]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c1].[KichThuoc], [c0].[MaDH], [c0].[MaChiTiet], [c1].[MaChiTiet] AS [MaChiTiet0], [c1].[MaSanPham]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c0]

) AS [t0] ON [d].[MaDH] = [t0].[MaDH]
LEFT JOIN [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c2] ON [d].[MaDH] = [c2].[MaDH]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s0].[MaSanPham], [c3].[MaDH], [c3].[MaChiTiet]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c3]
    INNER JOIN [SanPham] AS [s0] ON [c3].[MaSanPham] = [s0].[MaSanPham]
) AS [t1] ON [d].[MaDH] = [t1].[MaDH]

SELECT [d].[DanhGia], [d].[BinhLuan], [d].[id] AS [Id], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c0].[KichThuoc]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [ChiTietKichThuoc] AS [c0] ON ([c].[MaSanPham] = [c0].[MaSanPham]) AND ([c].[MaChiTiet] = [c0].[MaChiTiet])
    WHERE [c].[MaDH] = [d].[MaDH]) AS [KichThuoc], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [c1].[SoLuong]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c1]
    WHERE ([c1].[MaDH] = [d].[MaDH]) AND ([c1].[MaSanPham] = [d].[MaSanPham])), 0) AS [SoLuong], [d].[HinhAnh], [d].[NgayDanhGia], [d].[MaSanPham], [t0].[HoTen] AS [TenKhachHang], (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [DanhGiaSP] AS [d0]
    WHERE [d0].[MaSanPham] = [d].[MaSanPham]) AS [LuotDanhGia], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[PhanHoi]
    FROM [PhanHoiDanhGia] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[MaDanhGia] = [d].[MaDanhGia]) AS [PhanHoi], (
    SELECT COALESCE(SUM([c2].[SoLuong]), 0)
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c2]
    INNER JOIN [DonHang] AS [d1] ON [c2].[MaDH] = [d1].[MaDH]
    WHERE ([c2].[MaSanPham] = @__maSP_0) AND (([d1].[TrangThaiDH] = N'Đã đánh giá') OR (([d1].[TrangThaiDH] = N'Đã Thanh Toán') AND [d1].[ThongTinDH] IN (N'Đã Giao', N'Đang Giao')))) AS [LuotMua]
FROM [DanhGiaSP] AS [d]
INNER JOIN [TaiKhoan] AS [t] ON [d].[id] = [t].[id]
INNER JOIN [ThongTinCaNhan] AS [t0] ON [t].[idTK] = [t0].[idTK]
WHERE [d].[MaSanPham] = @__maSP_0

SELECT [c].[MaChiTietGiam], [c].[MaSanPham], [c].[MaVoucher], [c].[Slug], [c].[TenGiamGia], [k].[MaVoucher], [t].[MaSanPham], [t].[Gia], [t].[HinhAnh], [t].[MaBoSuuTap], [t].[MaChiTietGiam], [t].[MaLoaiSP], [t].[MaVatLieu], [t].[MoTa], [t].[TenSanPham], [t].[MaLoaiSP0], [t].[Slug], [t].[TenLoaiSP], [k].[GhiChu], [k].[id], [k].[PhanTramGiam], [k].[SoLan], [k].[TenChuongTrinh], [k].[ThoiGianBatDau], [k].[ThoiGianKetThuc]
FROM [ChiTietKhuyenMai] AS [c]
INNER JOIN [KhuyenMai] AS [k] ON [c].[MaVoucher] = [k].[MaVoucher]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s].[MaSanPham], [s].[Gia], [s].[HinhAnh], [s].[MaBoSuuTap], [s].[MaChiTietGiam], [s].[MaLoaiSP], [s].[MaVatLieu], [s].[MoTa], [s].[TenSanPham], [l].[MaLoaiSP] AS [MaLoaiSP0], [l].[Slug], [l].[TenLoaiSP]
    FROM [SanPham] AS [s]
    INNER JOIN [LoaiSP] AS [l] ON [s].[MaLoaiSP] = [l].[MaLoaiSP]
) AS [t] ON ([c].[MaChiTietGiam] = [t].[MaChiTietGiam]) AND ([c].[MaSanPham] = [t].[MaSanPham])
ORDER BY [c].[MaChiTietGiam], [c].[MaSanPham], [k].[MaVoucher], [t].[MaSanPham]

SELECT [c].[MaChiTietGiam], [c].[MaSanPham], [c].[MaVoucher], [c].[Slug], [c].[TenGiamGia], [k].[MaVoucher], [t].[MaSanPham], [t].[Gia], [t].[HinhAnh], [t].[MaBoSuuTap], [t].[MaChiTietGiam], [t].[MaLoaiSP], [t].[MaVatLieu], [t].[MoTa], [t].[TenSanPham], [t].[MaLoaiSP0], [t].[Slug], [t].[TenLoaiSP], [k].[GhiChu], [k].[id], [k].[PhanTramGiam], [k].[SoLan], [k].[TenChuongTrinh], [k].[ThoiGianBatDau], [k].[ThoiGianKetThuc]
FROM [ChiTietKhuyenMai] AS [c]
INNER JOIN [KhuyenMai] AS [k] ON [c].[MaVoucher] = [k].[MaVoucher]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s].[MaSanPham], [s].[Gia], [s].[HinhAnh], [s].[MaBoSuuTap], [s].[MaChiTietGiam], [s].[MaLoaiSP], [s].[MaVatLieu], [s].[MoTa], [s].[TenSanPham], [l].[MaLoaiSP] AS [MaLoaiSP0], [l].[Slug], [l].[TenLoaiSP]
    FROM [SanPham] AS [s]
    INNER JOIN [LoaiSP] AS [l] ON [s].[MaLoaiSP] = [l].[MaLoaiSP]
) AS [t] ON ([c].[MaChiTietGiam] = [t].[MaChiTietGiam]) AND ([c].[MaSanPham] = [t].[MaSanPham])
ORDER BY [c].[MaChiTietGiam], [c].[MaSanPham], [k].[MaVoucher], [t].[MaSanPham]

SELECT [c].[MaChiTietGiam], [c].[MaSanPham], [c].[MaVoucher], [c].[Slug], [c].[TenGiamGia], [k].[MaVoucher], [t].[MaSanPham], [t].[Gia], [t].[HinhAnh], [t].[MaBoSuuTap], [t].[MaChiTietGiam], [t].[MaLoaiSP], [t].[MaVatLieu], [t].[MoTa], [t].[TenSanPham], [t].[MaLoaiSP0], [t].[Slug], [t].[TenLoaiSP], [k].[GhiChu], [k].[id], [k].[PhanTramGiam], [k].[SoLan], [k].[TenChuongTrinh], [k].[ThoiGianBatDau], [k].[ThoiGianKetThuc]
FROM [ChiTietKhuyenMai] AS [c]
INNER JOIN [KhuyenMai] AS [k] ON [c].[MaVoucher] = [k].[MaVoucher]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s].[MaSanPham], [s].[Gia], [s].[HinhAnh], [s].[MaBoSuuTap], [s].[MaChiTietGiam], [s].[MaLoaiSP], [s].[MaVatLieu], [s].[MoTa], [s].[TenSanPham], [l].[MaLoaiSP] AS [MaLoaiSP0], [l].[Slug], [l].[TenLoaiSP]
    FROM [SanPham] AS [s]
    INNER JOIN [LoaiSP] AS [l] ON [s].[MaLoaiSP] = [l].[MaLoaiSP]
) AS [t] ON ([c].[MaChiTietGiam] = [t].[MaChiTietGiam]) AND ([c].[MaSanPham] = [t].[MaSanPham])
ORDER BY [c].[MaChiTietGiam], [c].[MaSanPham], [k].[MaVoucher], [t].[MaSanPham]

SELECT [c].[MaChiTietGiam], [c].[MaSanPham], [c].[MaVoucher], [c].[Slug], [c].[TenGiamGia], [k].[MaVoucher], [t].[MaSanPham], [t].[Gia], [t].[HinhAnh], [t].[MaBoSuuTap], [t].[MaChiTietGiam], [t].[MaLoaiSP], [t].[MaVatLieu], [t].[MoTa], [t].[TenSanPham], [t].[MaLoaiSP0], [t].[Slug], [t].[TenLoaiSP], [k].[GhiChu], [k].[id], [k].[PhanTramGiam], [k].[SoLan], [k].[TenChuongTrinh], [k].[ThoiGianBatDau], [k].[ThoiGianKetThuc]
FROM [ChiTietKhuyenMai] AS [c]
INNER JOIN [KhuyenMai] AS [k] ON [c].[MaVoucher] = [k].[MaVoucher]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s].[MaSanPham], [s].[Gia], [s].[HinhAnh], [s].[MaBoSuuTap], [s].[MaChiTietGiam], [s].[MaLoaiSP], [s].[MaVatLieu], [s].[MoTa], [s].[TenSanPham], [l].[MaLoaiSP] AS [MaLoaiSP0], [l].[Slug], [l].[TenLoaiSP]
    FROM [SanPham] AS [s]
    INNER JOIN [LoaiSP] AS [l] ON [s].[MaLoaiSP] = [l].[MaLoaiSP]
) AS [t] ON ([c].[MaChiTietGiam] = [t].[MaChiTietGiam]) AND ([c].[MaSanPham] = [t].[MaSanPham])
ORDER BY [c].[MaChiTietGiam], [c].[MaSanPham], [k].[MaVoucher], [t].[MaSanPham]

INNER JOIN [KhuyenMai] AS [k] ON [c].[MaVoucher] = [k].[MaVoucher]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s].[MaSanPham], [s].[Gia], [s].[HinhAnh], [s].[MaBoSuuTap], [s].[MaChiTietGiam], [s].[MaLoaiSP], [s].[MaVatLieu], [s].[MoTa], [s].[TenSanPham], [l].[MaLoaiSP] AS [MaLoaiSP0], [l].[Slug], [l].[TenLoaiSP]
    FROM [SanPham] AS [s]
    INNER JOIN [LoaiSP] AS [l] ON [s].[MaLoaiSP] = [l].[MaLoaiSP]
) AS [t] ON ([c].[MaChiTietGiam] = [t].[MaChiTietGiam]) AND ([c].[MaSanPham] = [t].[MaSanPham])

FROM [ChiTietKhuyenMai] AS [c]
INNER JOIN [KhuyenMai] AS [k] ON [c].[MaVoucher] = [k].[MaVoucher]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s].[MaSanPham], [s].[Gia], [s].[HinhAnh], [s].[MaBoSuuTap], [s].[MaChiTietGiam], [s].[MaLoaiSP], [s].[MaVatLieu], [s].[MoTa], [s].[TenSanPham], [l].[MaLoaiSP] AS [MaLoaiSP0], [l].[Slug], [l].[TenLoaiSP]
    FROM [SanPham] AS [s]
    INNER JOIN [LoaiSP] AS [l] ON [s].[MaLoaiSP] = [l].[MaLoaiSP]
) AS [t] ON ([c].[MaChiTietGiam] = [t].[MaChiTietGiam]) AND ([c].[MaSanPham] = [t].[MaSanPham])
ORDER BY [c].[MaChiTietGiam], [c].[MaSanPham], [k].[MaVoucher], [t].[MaSanPham]

    SELECT TOP(1) (
        SELECT TOP(1) [t2].[TenDangNhap]
        FROM [TaiKhoan] AS [t2]
        WHERE [t2].[id] = [g].[id])
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c4]
    INNER JOIN [GioHang] AS [g] ON [c4].[MaGioHang] = [g].[MaGioHang]
    WHERE [c4].[MaDH] = [d].[MaDH])
FROM [DonHang] AS [d]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s].[TenSanPham], [c].[MaDH], [c].[MaChiTiet], [s].[MaSanPham]
    FROM [ChiTietDonHang] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [SanPham] AS [s] ON [c].[MaSanPham] = [s].[MaSanPham]
